Package com.google.code.ssm.config

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AddressChangeListener
    Changes addresses of cache servers.
    AddressChangeNotifier
    Notifies associated AddressChangeListener about changes of servers' addresses.
    AddressProvider
    Provides addresses of cache servers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSSMConfiguration
    Basic xml-less configuration of SSM.
    DefaultAddressProvider
    Address provider that can be used to configure addresses of memcached servers as a string with comma or whitespace separated addresses: "host:port host2:port" or "host:port,host2:port".
    JndiAddressProvider
    Gets servers' addresses from JNDI defined under key JndiAddressProvider.getJndiKey().
